  "description": "A crushed-salt constitutive model is implemented in FLAC3D / 3DEC to simulate volumetric and deviatoric creep compaction behaviors. The model is a variation of the WIPP model , and is based on the model described by Sjaardema and Krieg (1987), with an added deviatoric component as proposed by Callahan and DeVries (1991).",
